    • hopitalizationPet

      public java.lang.String hopitalizationPet()
      This method takes care of sending a hospitalized pet to the day care center. pre:The habitat matrix is initialized, all counter variables are initialized. pos:In case there is space, the pet will stay in the first habitat that has a null pet.
      Returns:
      ; returns a message indicating whether or not the pet entered the day care center

    • addPetToNursery

      public java.lang.String addPetToNursery​(java.lang.String specie, java.lang.String name, java.lang.String age, java.lang.String race, java.lang.String nameOwn, java.lang.String idOwn, java.lang.String phoneOwn, java.lang.String addressOwn)
      This method is responsible for entering a pet into the day care. pre: The habitats and counter variables are initialized. pos: The pet remains in the first habitat with pet null and that is in the limits according to its species.
      Parameters:
      specie - A string with the pet's species
      name - A string with the pet's name
      age - A string with the pet's age
      race - A string with the pet's race
      nameOwn - A string with the pet owner's name on it
      idOwn - A string with the pet owner's id on it
      phoneOwn - A string with the pet owner's phone on it
      addreessOwn - A String with the pet owner's name on it
      Returns:
      A string indicating whether or not the pet was able to enter the nursery.
